Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.52,0:03:34.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Tam sú! Našiel som ich!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.02,0:03:35.86,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Vyzdvihneme ich?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.07,0:03:38.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nie, choď tesne popri nich. Použijeme auto ako štít.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.24,0:03:43.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Máme tu živý prídavok, Chinatsu.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.82,0:03:46.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Je čas to urýchliť!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.33,0:03:49.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Negev?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.58,0:03:51.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Má Negev LMG!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.25,0:03:53.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,To je...
