Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.73,0:22:23.32,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\be1\c&H3C5B8B&}Thinking of the bundles of documents
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.73,0:22:23.32,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\an8\be1\c&HAC8455&}omoi haseru kiroku no taba
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.32,0:22:30.57,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1\c&H3C5B8B&}Sweet poison entangles my arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:23.32,0:22:30.57,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an8\be1\c&HAC8455&}amai doku ga ude ni karamu
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.57,0:22:37.83,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1\c&H3C5B8B&}I had seen a particular dream,\Nwhere we we'd be one step closer,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:30.57,0:22:37.83,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an8\be1\c&HAC8455&}yomitoketa nara chikatzukeru to
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.83,0:22:43.34,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\be1\c&H3C5B8B&}if we had understood each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.83,0:22:43.34,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(0,200)\an8\be1\c&HAC8455&}sonna yume wo mita
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.21,0:22:52.72,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\be1\c&H3C5B8B&}The flowers had withered, leaving the seeds behind
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.21,0:22:52.72,ED,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,0)\an8\be1\c&HAC8455&}hana wa karete tane wo nokoshi
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.72,0:23:00.06,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1\c&H3C5B8B&\t(\c&HC8BCB0&\3c&H000000&)}And even if it's an everlasting process,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.72,0:23:00.06,ED,,0,0,0,,{\an8\be1\c&HAC8455&\t(\c&HC8BCB0&\3c&H000000&)}tsutzuite yuku mono dakeredo
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.06,0:23:17.20,ED,,0,0,0,,{\be1\fad(0,200)\c&HC8BCB0&\3c&H000000&}These white flowers could do\Nnothing but bloom on a single stump.
